          The majority of my work and project experience has involved combining software and hardware for developing robotic 
          platforms along with developing software for various applications. I also have experience with full-cycle design, 
          integration, and testing of robotic platforms. I have taken multiple leadership roles in teams ranging from 4 to 100 
          student and professional members, and have additional experience with project management, product development, 
          sponsorship, and website development.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Divider Line -->
      <div class="w-full h-px bg-white/30 mb-12"></div>

